    <h4>Postgraduate Programs</h4>
    <p>
      CLCS offers postgraduate programs focusing on Bhutanese language, culture, Buddhist studies, Himalayan studies, and Gross National Happiness (GNH) studies. For detailed information, please visit the official CLCS website.
    </p>

    <hr style="margin: 1.5rem 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />

    <h4>Admission Information</h4>
    <p>
      Admissions for undergraduate programs require applicants to have passed Class XII with specific criteria depending on the program. For instance, the BA in Dzongkha and Culture Studies requires a pass mark in English, making it more inclusive for students with a strong background in Dzongkha.
    </p>

    <h4>Funding Options</h4>
